{"tid":1286803,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"譴責7月1日示威者的暴力行為聯署聲明","createTime":"2019-07-05T03:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T04:23:09.000Z","uid":2552,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a4313411d6d5fe25ae5045fb2624adc64fc03ec","tid":1286803,"uid":2552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"屌係facebook見到藍絲share <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以點玩 見佢剩係打名就得<br />\n但又唔想俾咁多數字佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n譴責7月1日示威者的暴力行為聯署聲明<br />\n我們是一群真心熱愛香港的小市民，香港一直是全球最安全城市之一，市民都能和平、理性地表達意見。但2019年7月1日凌晨起，金鐘、灣仔一帶有大批示威者佔據主要交通幹道，設置路障蓄意阻塞往來交通；同時有人在立法會廣場，把國旗換上印有洋紫荊圖案的黑旗，並將特區區旗「下半旗」。有示威者腐蝕性液體潑向警察。<br />\n直到傍晚，一班暴徒破壞立法會的玻璃門、鐵閘，衝入立法會，大肆破壞立法會內所有的設施。<br />\n<br />\n我們對以上一切的暴力行為，予以強烈譴責，香港容不下如此暴力的行為，請停止破壞香港，讓香港盡快回復和平、理性。<br />\n<br />\n傳送門:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeJdF3DAgcmLEW35G3Oaj7Yyebg6XirKB3rbokUggauNXJuBg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeJdF3DAgcmLEW35G3Oaj7Yyebg6XirKB3rbokUggauNXJuBg%2Fviewform&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=7894a013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeJdF3DAgcmLEW35G3Oaj7Yyebg6XirKB3rbokUggauNXJuBg/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"983085c14bd38b082febd4e662bb678ed9200be6","tid":1286803,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"Ignore, 呢啲數字係冇用"},{"pid":"6ecdd844b754e6fee4ce9cc3612ff1c743a10d0d","tid":1286803,"uid":23189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:29:26.000Z","msg":"「七黑」團結打倒白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284973\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284973</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zm1ytZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzm1ytZc.jpg&h=68603869&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0414d5771399b38469e04e2ba344232175bd7cf7","tid":1286803,"uid":91897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"暴力，但無人傷亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21a837207f530b56f0d00606a67fd42b669d266","tid":1286803,"uid":163082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:30:25.000Z","msg":"屌，望到d簽名，交一億個都得啦，陳小姐 李先生咁都算？無人識你啊"},{"pid":"4b210bd5449619edaa2ac8220e37c05ea05b756f","tid":1286803,"uid":2552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"983085c14bd38b082febd4e662bb678ed9200be6","tid":1286803,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"Ignore, 呢啲數字係冇用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:33:11.000Z","msg":"咁我係咪應該宣揚一吓支持成立獨立調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47c9ba8d978a42cf995ac21647510003218350a","tid":1286803,"uid":91897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"唔搞番個譴責630撐警人士暴力行為聯署聲明？<br />\n有女記者比人非禮，有１５歲女比人打裂鼻骨，立法會議員被打<br />\n根本班人渣活係自己世界拎Ｄ數字打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4b2a98abbf84ce8ede5b5d79c1f902c70c707a","tid":1286803,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:22:44.000Z","msg":"入d古人既名入去"},{"pid":"d8d2ef827ae1aaaf5af587d335b324f0728e20e5","tid":1286803,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e4b2a98abbf84ce8ede5b5d79c1f902c70c707a","tid":1286803,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:22:44.000Z","msg":"入d古人既名入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:23:09.000Z","msg":"張飛 劉備 曹操"}]}